wikiPage.wikiPageContent:
Thank you for installing wiki.py! wiki.py is a wiki software made entirely with the Python console. This is the help page for it.

To add a page, do "addPage(pageName)". Keep in mind that the page will not be added if it already exists. To view a page, do "viewPage(pageName)". If you want to edit a page, do "editPage(pageName)".

Keep in mind that the edit function is still a WIP.
